advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References
description:
TouchTunes allows you to control the music in over 60,000 bars and restaurants in the US and Canada. The app acts as a remote jukebox allowing you to search songs and play the music in the bar from your mobile phone – wherever you are: on a bar stool, waiting in line or queuing your theme song from the parking lot! 
 
Features:
·      Find locations with TouchTunes near you
·      See what’s playing in the bar and what’s up next
·      See who else is checked in and what they’re playing
·      Get rewards and bonus credits the more you play
·      Become the House DJ
·      Buy and earn jukebox credits
·      Create playlists or sync your iPhone’s music collection to make it easier to find your favorite tracks
·      See your play history, most played and personal recommendations
·      Share where you are and what songs you're playing on Facebook, Twitter and Foursquare

Disclaimer:
Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

For updates on new music and exclusive artist performances, like us on Facebook.com/TouchTunes or follow us on Twitter.com/TouchTunes
 
If you have any feedback for our jukebox app please email us at mobilefeedback@touchtunes.com
